FBIS3-38512 "drweu023__a94010" FBIS-WEU-94-023-A Document Type:Daily Report 3 February 1994 ANNEX Italy & Vatican City President Scalfaro Reported Sick, Cancels Meetings BR0202140094 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1236 GMT 2 Feb 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY BR0202140094 Rome ANSAMAIL Database Language: English Article Type:BFN [Unattributed article: "Scalfaro Takes Week's Sick Leave"] [Text] Rome, 2 Feb (ANSA) -- It was confirmed this morning that President Oscar Luigi Scalfaro has been forced to take a week off duty by an attack of "acute bronchitis with a high fever." Scalfaro was rumoured to be sick when he cancelled official engagements on Monday [31 January] and Tuesday; doctors have now extended his sick leave until the end of the week.
